title: Quiz: How well do you know Frank Lampard's career?
text:
Frank Lampard has called time on his illustrious career.
Very few players have come anywhere near achieving what he has in terms of appearances or honours.
His career began at West Ham, before moving to Chelsea where he enjoyed enormous success, then followed shorter spells at both Manchester City and New York City before his retirement at the age of 38.
How many questions can you correctly answer in our challenging Frank Lampard career quiz?
He is also part of a very select group of players to earn more than 100 caps for England.
We've put together 20 questions on his career. How many can you get right?
